8: Whoa! You've been looking for me?
11:
You're... that cafe owner from White
Fest?
14:
Please, you have to help me! My
cafe's in trouble!
20:
So... After White Fest, your place was
popular enough to be put under the
Guild's management, but you have
a problem with their policy.
23:
I don't get it. Shouldn't you be
happy? They think you're good
enough to offer nicer service, yeah?
26:
If I start offering high-class food and
raise my prices, my regulars won't
be able to come anymore! This'll kill
my business!
29:
Hmm. I believe you are in the wrong
here.
32:
Considering the changes in the
economy and taxes, the numbers
your manager gave are reasonable.
34:
Or are you that opposed to
increasing the quality of your goods
and services?
39:
The most important thing is that
your regulars keep coming back,
yes?
42:
Because even if you avoid making
changes to your business, there's no
guarantee they'll return.
44:
However, I have a few ideas to turn
things around.
49:
Of course. Just so you know, she
used to be the boss of a huge
company.
52:
You'll be in good hands. Could you
tell me more about what you did for
White Fest?
56: I believe I can give you the details.
61:
Hello, my friend. If you were in such
a pinch, you should've reached out
to me.
65:
You were definitely listening in this
whole time with your shikigami,
weren't you...
68:
Oh, perish the thought. I just
happened to be nearby to observe
the Halloween festivities.
71:
Well, Love, I hope you won't mind if I
join as your new partner in crime.
76:
Not at all. Your assistance is much
appreciated.
87:
Today we're offering a Trick Course...
It includes dishes sure to shock your
taste buds...
91:
Or you could have our Treat Course!
It's filled with tasty sweets and tea to
cleanse the palate!
98:
We also offer a discount to
customers dressed up for
Halloween. Please, have a seat and
enjoy yourself.
101:
Hey, this is pretty good. I didn't know
you could cook stuff like this.
102:
Eh, since it's Halloween, I should
splurge a little... Can I have one of
these cakes to go? I wanna share
some with my kid!
107:
Wow... I mean, I figured you'd get the
job done, but it's still impressive.
110:
It all starts with making it easy for
first-timers to walk in. The rest will
follow.
113:
Hehe, this has proved to be a
valuable experience for my future
business expansion plans...
119:
Now that sounds like something I'd
be interested in.
122:
Excellent work today, making sure
both the owner and customers have
their demands met.
126:
You came up with the original plan.
The credit goes to you. I would be
pleased to count on your assistance
in the future.
130:
But of course! We should invite Regis
as well. He has quite the plethora of
experience and connections.
134:
This is starting to look like a
gathering of super villains...
138:
By the way... Why did you offer your
help so freely?
141:
Haha, you think there's some ulterior
motive? Pretty sure she did it just
'cause she wanted to help.
145:
Partly, yes. After all, Bulleta would've
chosen to help.
148:
...I was also motivated by sympathy.
I know what it's like to fear change
and be frustrated when things don't
go the way I want.
152:
Good thing you were able to turn it
around.
157:
I couldn't have done it alone. Thank
you all for helping too.
161:
Love, we got a customer here who
wants a picture with you!
164: ...We'll take it for you. Over here.
172:
I see... I was mistaken in my
assumption.
178:
Lately, I keep thinking about how I'm
always being saved by others.
181:
I'm grateful to have such
dependable people at my side, but I
feel my powerlessness all the more
for it.
183:
...I was even saved by the people I
was supposed to be leading.
185:
On top of that, the abilities that DAN
gave me were meant to be used for
the company's sake.
187: It feels wrong to still have them.
193:
Besides, it's not like you can just get
rid of them.
199:
...There are so many things I could
never let go of.
202:
But thanks to that, I was able to help
someone today.
205:
Everything I received from DAN, from
you, from Bulleta... They continue to
live on in me.
207:
I still have a long way to go before I
can do something like save the
world, but today I was able to make
a difference for at least one person.
